quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  4,114,"La khayra fee katheerin min najwahumilla man amara bisadaqatin aw maAAroofin aw islahinbayna annasi waman yafAAal thalika ibtighaamardati Allahi fasawfa nu/teehi ajran AAatheema"
  4,115,"Waman yushaqiqi arrasoolamin baAAdi ma tabayyana lahu alhuda wayattabiAAghayra sabeeli almu/mineena nuwallihi ma tawallawanuslihi jahannama wasaat maseera"
  4,116,"Inna Allaha la yaghfiru anyushraka bihi wayaghfiru ma doona thalika limanyashao waman yushrik billahi faqad dalladalalan baAAeeda"
  4,117,"In yadAAoona min doonihi illa inathanwa-in yadAAoona illa shaytanan mareeda"
  4,118,"LaAAanahu Allahu waqalalaattakhithanna min AAibadika naseebanmafrooda"
  4,119,"Walaodillannahum walaomanniyannahumwalaamurannahum falayubattikunna athana al-anAAamiwalaamurannahum falayughayyirunna khalqa Allahiwaman yattakhithi ashshaytana waliyyan mindooni Allahi faqad khasira khusranan mubeena"
  4,120,"YaAAiduhum wayumanneehim wamayaAAiduhumu ashshaytanu illa ghuroora"
  4,121,"Ola-ika ma/wahum jahannamuwala yajidoona AAanha maheesa"
